<title>Camping Equipment - Retail Camping Company</title>
</head>
<body>
<header>
<div class="nav-container">
<img src="C:/Users/Kaddra52/Desktop/DDW/assets/images/logo.svg" alt="Logo" class="logo">
<h1>Retail Camping Company</h1>
